{
  "stem": "8786.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I would-- And there was another thing which I've seen in Malthausen.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "While we were sitting, all of the sudden, boom!",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "One of those guys in the tower wanted to try out how he can shoot.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he shot-- and he just-- into the crowd.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And so it happened that the men who got a bullet into his brain was about two yards away from me.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So when the brain splashed out, I was full.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he had a brother there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And that brother looked at his-- this man was shaking for the rest of the day because he was dead right away, brain dead, but the whole body was shaking like this.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And the pieces of the brain, I'm telling you, was splashing all over.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I remember his brother, he tried to empty out his pocket.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He knew that they're going to take him away soon.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Every few minutes-- few hours, you have seen those dead carriages with carrying half dead or totally dead people, they were just like pieces of-- you probably have seen this in the magazines and English films, how those camps looked with those skinny, no flesh but bones.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Anyway, this man was taking out, was crying.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We were also crying for him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Because I've seen the decent, the human part of it that he takes out from his brother's pocket, the pictures.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And whatever he had in his pocket, he took it out, emptied it out.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And a few minutes later-- But it was a whole day the man was shaking.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And because just one of those animals over there wanted to try out his pistol or his gun.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "This is what I remember from Malthausen.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "We didn't work.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
